74	// The Claude SDK persists local slash command invocations (e.g. `/model`) and
75	// their output as user messages in the session transcript, wrapping the
76	// payload in these XML-like markers that the CLI uses for its own display.
77	// The live prompt loop drops them; replay must strip them too or they leak
